ting a co-infection rate of 35.2% (95% CI = 26.8-43.6%).\nConclusion: The data highlights the H. capsulatum and Pneumocystis spp.co-infection in bat population's suggesting interplay with this wild host.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Gonz\u00e1lez-Gonz\u00e1lez, Antonio E", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aliouat-Denis, C\u00e9cile M", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ram\u00edrez-B\u00e1rcenas, Jos\u00e9 A", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Demanche, Christine", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pottier, Muriel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Carreto-Binaghi, Laura E", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Akbar, Haroon", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Derouiche, Sandra", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Chab\u00e9, Magalie", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Aliouat, El Moukhtar", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dei-Cas, Eduardo", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Taylor, Maria Lucia", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/aea8972b6d20098aa31ff824f915edb3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/645dda1143af480f71056a5a5ce258d1bf65acbd34caeceb2aa3d43da2cb850d", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/ZWW7B9ZK", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/ZWW7B9ZK", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/c2ede67dcd6f6da08a34b72cb867016a!/b347254-349850", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/330417efcaa2560c9b8ebcd6fae17ce0", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:ph